data.description: If comfort, the convenience of move in ready and functionality are what you are looking for in your home, look no further. This move in ready 3-bed, 4-bath, 2-story home with a finished basement is awaiting you! You have the option to entertain effortlessly in the open-concept living and dining areas, complemented by a spacious kitchen boasting ample cabinets and granite countertops  with the luxury of a large double door pantry boasting plenty of storage space. Enjoy the warmth of a gas fireplace and the comfort of a natural gas generator for any electrical outage. The main bedroom suite features a 21x11 bonus room, perfect for your personalized retreat. With an audio/intercom system and security cameras you are ensured a peace of mind knowing you can stay connected with the homes surroundings. Many upgrades including ceiling fans, light fixtures and a sump pump don't just make this a home, but a haven of style and functionality. Seize the day and schedule your showing now!
